"{\"uid\": \"thechronicle.com.gh-djokovic-beats-nadal-to-keep-olympic-dream-going\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Novak Djokovic outclassed his long-time rival Rafael Nadal to win their Olympic second-round match and continue his bid to land an elusive gold medal.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 58, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Serbia's Djokovic, 37, looked on a different level to Nadal for most of a one-sided contest which he won 6-1 6-4 on the Roland Garros clay.\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 152, \"end\": 158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5601523401318751, \"rank\": 0.7847191976262281, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 161, \"end\": 169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9900803807492927, \"rank\": 0.010019003955228804, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 206, \"end\": 211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999995803094378, \"rank\": 4.1969076226211247e-07, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic led 4-0 in the second set to quell the partisan support for the Spaniard, before 38-year-old Nadal fought back to wipe out the double break.\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 366, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.9838823086245803, \"rank\": 0.014504881216130324, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Djokovic, like we have seen him do so many times, stepped on the gas again to break for 5-4 and serve out victory.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very relieved,\\\" said Djokovic.\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9900803807492927, \"rank\": 0.010019003955228804, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything was going my way, I was 6-1, 4-0 up but I played a sloppy service game and gave him chances.\\\"\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal, known as the King of Clay, has won 14 French Open titles at the Olympic venue but the aura he carries there was not enough to trouble a man of Djokovic's quality.\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 858, \"end\": 866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9900803807492927, \"rank\": 0.010019003955228804, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair, who have won 46 Grand Slam singles titles between them, shared an embrace at the net before Djokovic sportingly clapped Nadal off the court.\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 981, \"end\": 989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9900803807492927, \"rank\": 0.010019003955228804, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999995803094378, \"rank\": 4.1969076226211247e-07, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the 60th meeting of their enduring rivalry - no two men have ever played each other more.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After first meeting in 2006, Djokovic now leads 31-29 in their head to head.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9900803807492927, \"rank\": 0.010019003955228804, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never thought back in 2006 that we'd still be playing each other almost 20 years later,\\\" Djokovic said.\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1299, \"end\": 1307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9900803807492927, \"rank\": 0.010019003955228804, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Credit: bbc.com  Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u0394  Exchange RateUSD: Tue, 2 Dec.\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1447, \"entities\": []}]}"